{
  "stem": "23428.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We never wore yellow stars, because we felt [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so strongly that this was not our identity.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So-- but all of my classmates with whom I made the baccalaureate wore the yellow star and were ghettoized, which of course, we were not either, until our arrest, which came [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for my father, a few days after the 20th of July putsch, and for us, maybe two weeks later.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had-- well, maybe not friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I had certainly at least a couple of Jewish classmates.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not sure really whether these were religious Jews either.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were certainly ethnic Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No, maybe not even that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were probably ethnic Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's very hard to-- to say that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All I know is that under that legislation, everybody was defined by the religion of their grandparents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were Jews just like us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- we lived a perfectly [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] independent life until the days of our arrest in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] maybe I should start out with the arrest of my father, because that preceded everything else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think our arrest came under the general heading of Sippenhaft, the responsibility of the family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was one of the fascist views, that whenever anybody was punished for one reason or another, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the family also had a responsibility.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if the father was shot, usually wife and children and babies, everybody was shot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, well, my father's story [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] actually goes back a few years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think it's-- I can't explain his arrest without explaining what preceded it.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
